Most of my projects can be found on my GitHub account. I have worked on many group and personal projects. I've also contributed to some open source projects like OWASP SecureTea, ns-3-AppStore, bake. Open Telemetry. My bachelors' thesis work on DPDK power measurement is published and can be found here. Most of them involved using the following technologies or languages:

Languages

C, C++, Python, Erlang, JavaScript, HTML, CSS

DBMS

MySQL, NoSQL (MongoDB)

Tools/Frameworks

MEAN Stack, Django, Git, OpenMP, jQuery, Laravel, Ruby on Rails, STL, ns-3, Gatsby, AWS, pktgen-dpdk

If you've a project idea, feel free to connect and we can discuss!
